# _Cheap Online_ Custom Sticker Printing In Canada

###### Leading sticker printing specialist at the most affordable cost. Your
one-stop-shop for quality custom stickers for all sorts of needs.

Welcome to StickerCanada where design and printing custom stickers is our
expertise. Whether promoting your business, brands, products, and services,
not to mention that it's also applicable as giveaways on an event, birthday,
wedding, christening, and other DIY projects. We live to meet your
expectations either for personal or business needs.

Our custom printed stickers are made of high-quality materials at the cheapest

marketing and creative expression. With the support of our skilled designers,

specifications.

We are proud of our secured delivery system: Quick, Efficient, and FREE

## Classic Paper Stickers

### Premium quality writable sticker

Printed in a non-lustrous surface material  
making it the best option for writing purposes.  
It has an elegant appearance and an excellent way of customizing packaging
labels.

For this sticker material, please be informed that the material base is off
white,  
therefore a possible color gap may occur.

## Foil Stamp

### Start looking fab with your branding!

A printing method in which a metal foil is transferred by heat and pressure.  
This process brings out a feeling of luxury and presents a lavish look  
that cannot be expressed by normal printing.

### COLOR

Gold/Silver/Hologram/Black are popular colors.

Other colors for foil are available upon request.

 **0 1**

## White Print

### Infinite range of expression by combining white print

White printing is used to solidify the colors of the design  
in a transparent sticker or a material  
with dark colors like Kraft Paper Stickers.

### No White print

The ink will be transparent. Depending on the material or surface to be  
printed, The color of the design looks different.

### White Print

Because the ink can be softened, it can be printed on a material or a paste  
surface. It can fully express the color of the design without being
influenced.

 **0 1**

## Sheet Supply

### Fit sticker designs as many possibilities

A special process for stickers to fit on single or multiple sheets by having a
theme of designs  
Supplied on kiss-cut that is best recommended for easy peeling stickers  
on a sheet and works great to customize labels.
